data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3/2/2 located in the Uptown West Subdivision of Frenship ISD.  The soaring ceilings of this home offers a beautifully designed floor to ceiling  fireplace accented with patterned tile and shiplap. A large, sunny patio door leads outside to the backyard.   The kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, and an abundance of counter space with seating for 4. With stainless appliances, gorgeous granite counters and a walk-in pantry, your friends and family are sure to be delighted. Bright windows highlight the dining area. The isolated primary suite features double vanities with a makeup dressing area, separate soaking tub, generous shower and a extra large closet with built ins.  The other two bedrooms share an oversized bath with double lavatories.  Outside you find a patio area that is perfect for entertaining and a dog run with storage shed.
